query.sfwSql: SELECT * FROM SGT_WSS_EMPLOYMENT_CHANGE_REQUEST WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE STATUS_VALUE IN ('REVW','RJTD')
select * from sgs_code_value where code_id = 3510 and isnull(data1,'') = 'DV' order by 1
select * from sgt_organization B where A.org_id=B.Org_id

SELECT *, REQ.MODIFIED_BY AS istrRejectedByName FROM SGT_WSS_EMPLOYMENT_CHANGE_REQUEST REQ WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER ON REQ.PERSON_ID=PER.PERSON_ID WHERE STATUS_VALUE IN ('REVW','RJTD') and ORG_ID=@ORGID AND DATEDIFF(d,REQ.MODIFIED_DATE,GETDATE()) <=90
